      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup by second analyst; boundary conditions and material assignments verified against test protocol.",
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by second FEA engineer not involved in original construction. Boundary conditions (fixed base, displacement-controlled loading at superior vertebral body block) verified against ASTM F1717 test protocol. Material assignments cross-checked against coupon test data. Required level 2 achieved."
