      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from coupon tests on same material lot; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa) and Poisson ratio (0.34) for Ti-6Al-4V sourced from tensile coupon tests on same material lot as test constructs. UHMWPE block modulus (0.95 GPa) from compression coupon tests. Screw geometry from CMM measurements (±0.01 mm). Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=500); 95th-percentile QoI spread <4%. Required level 3 achieved."
