      "acceptanceCriteria": "Multiple loading rates and environmental conditions tested; test conditions fully characterized and replicated in FEA.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) under ambient laboratory conditions only. No variation in loading rate, temperature, or humidity explored. This single test condition limits confidence in model generalizability across the loading rate spectrum. Achieved level 2 falls below required level 3; this shortfall is noted as a credibility gap but does not preclude acceptance given medium model influence and corroborating multi-laboratory data.",
