      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions derived directly from ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry and measured specimen dimensions. Material property inputs traceable to same material lot as test specimens via material certification records. Equivalency between experimental and simulation inputs formally documented in the V&V report. Required level 3 achieved."
    },
