      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for stiffness (1.41), yield force (1.18), and force at 40 mm (1.55). All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. Relative errors all <10%. Quantitative comparison supports model adequacy claim. Required level 3 achieved."
