    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single quasi-static loading rate; this gap is accepted given medium model influence, medium decision consequence, corroborating multi-laboratory experimental data (N=11), and all quantitative comparison metrics (E/uval) satisfying the <1.96 acceptance criterion across all three QoIs. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim.",
